  "remarks": "Irina Ageeva is the Commissioner for Children’s Rights in Kaluga Region. In this role, she is one of the most involved persons in the illegal deportation of Ukrainian children to Russia and their adoption by Russian families. Irina Ageeva’s actions violate the rights of Ukrainian children and infringe Ukraine’s law and administrative order.",
